first-post",false,"Welcome to my blog! This is the first post.\n\n## What's This About?\n\nThis is a minimal Astro blog, deployed to GitHub Pages.\n\n### Writing in Markdown\n\nYou can use **bold**, *italic*, `code`, and all the standard markdown syntax.\n\n```javascript\n// code blocks work too\nconsole.log('Hello from the blog!');\n```\n\n> Blockquotes for emphasis.\n\nI'm looking forward to writing more here.","src/content/blog/hello-world.md","4b38f630da3c9a35",{"html":26,"metadata":27},"\u003Cp>Welcome to my blog! This is the first post.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"whats-this-about\">What’s This About?\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>This is a minimal Astro blog, deployed to GitHub Pages.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"writing-in-markdown\">Writing in Markdown\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>You can use \u003Cstrong>bold\u003C/strong>, \u003Cem>italic\u003C/em>, \u003Ccode>code\u003C/code>, and all the standard markdown syntax.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cpre class=\"astro-code github-dark\" style=\"background-color:#24292e;color:#e1e4e8; overflow-x: auto;\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"javascript\">\u003Ccode>\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#6A737D\">// code blocks work too\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\n\u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">console.\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#B392F0\">log\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">(\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#9ECBFF\">'Hello from the blog!'\u003C/span>\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">);\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/code>\u003C/pre>\n\u003Cblockquote>\n\u003Cp>Blockquotes for emphasis.\u003C/p>\n\u003C/blockquote>\n\u003Cp>I’m looking forward to writing more here.\u003C/p>",{"headings":28,"localImagePaths":37,"remoteImagePaths":38,"frontmatter":39,"imagePaths":42},[29,33],{"depth":30,"slug":31,"text":32},2,"whats-this-about","What’s This About?",{"depth":34,"slug":35,"text":36},3,"writing-in-markdown","Writing in Markdown",[],[],{"title":14,"date":40,"description":15,"category":17,"tags":41},["D